These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, turtle, cat, frog
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, malaysian, indian
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
3. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the indian is between the indonesian and the malaysian##2
6. the owner of the frog is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Pet   | frog | bird     | cat | turtle |
| Nationality     | argentine     | malaysian | indian  | indonesian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
4 different games are played: chess, go, bridge, snooker
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, firefighter, designer
1. the person playing go is on the left of the doctor##1
2. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the designer##1
4. the designer is on the right of the doctor##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
6. the dancer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Game   | chess | go    | snooker     | bridge  |
| Job     | dancer    | firefighter | doctor | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, argentine, british, indian
4 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, canasta, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the argentine##3
2. the argentine is on the far left##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the indian##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the australian##3
5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | argentine   | british   | australian  | indian |
| Game           | mah-jongg | snooker | canasta | monopoly  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
City: boston, edinburgh, hamburg, nizza
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, writer, scientist
1. the scientist is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to boston and the writer##2
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
4. the writer is on the left or right of the scientist##3
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the accountant is on the right of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| City         | edinburgh | boston | nizza | hamburg  |
| Job   | paramedic  | accountant   | scientist  | writer |

