.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pineapple, pear, peas
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, rose, orchid, poppy
1. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person who growspoppy is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Food   | asparagus    | pineapple   | pear | peas    |
| Flower      | rose | balloon-flower | orchid       | poppy |

