.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different games are played: domino, go, snooker, canasta
4 different pets are kept: snake, dog, goat, hamster
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the hamster and the person playing snooker##2
3. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the goat and the person playing domino##2
4. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Game    | domino | snooker | canasta | go |
| Pet   | dog | snake  | goat    | hamster  |

