.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
House: tower, ranch-style, craftsman, wooden
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, hip-hop, metal, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the tower house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the craftsman house is between the ranch-style house and the wooden house##2
5. the fan of hip-hop is the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of metal and the wooden house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| House   | tower | wooden | craftsman | ranch-style     |
| Music-Genre     | indie | folk  | hip-hop   | metal |

