.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, basketball, baseball
There 4 different types of food: onion, spinach, blueberry, pineapple
1. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating spinach##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | sailing | snowboarding   |
| Food   | spinach | blueberry | onion      | pineapple |

