2. the malaysian is on the far right##1
3. the malaysian is the victorian house##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the far left or far right##3
6. the gothic-revival house is between the thai and the brazilian##2

.:: Answer ::.
