.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, fanta, milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person driving the boat and the person driving the trike##2
3. the person drinking water is the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | tea | water | fanta      | milk   |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | trike    | skateboard | boat |

