.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, bird, frog, goat
House: victorian, gothic-revival, ranch-style, cape-cod
1. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the cape-cod house is the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
6. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Pet       | goldfish | frog | goat    | bird      |
| House   | ranch-style       | cape-cod       | gothic-revival | victorian |

