.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, water-polo, surfing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, october, july
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Sport   | biathlon     | rugby  | surfing | water-polo |
| Birthday     | april | july | december     | october    |

