.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, oliveros, alhambra, bluemaster
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, azalea, poppy, tulip
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the swisher-smoker is the swisher-smoker##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
6. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | swisher | alhambra  | bluemaster | oliveros |
| Flower           | poppy     | tulip | daffodil    | azalea     |

