2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
5. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | alhambra  | bolivar | blend  | game      |
| Beverage    | 7up | milk | mirinda | hot-chocolate |

