.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bolivar, siglo, pall-mall
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, dancing, camping
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Cigar   | bolivar     | alhambra     | siglo          | pall-mall |
| Hobby      | drawing | hiking | camping | dancing  |

 